reviewText: I  have always wanted that movie in dvd  It.s  agood mivie

Guys, this movie was intended to help get young men to volunteer for military duty during WW2. Well, besides accomplishing that, the script writers produced a product that was action packed but, which also had more than enough drama in it. The actors were great, even the dog!!
  This movie also has some actual war footage in it so, here';s even more to like about this movie. - Anonymouse
